	<h1 class="title">外资公司纷纷盯上了中国的“油盐酱醋”市场</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/517331/small/517331.jpg?1458028664" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">吴容 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-18 07:00:05 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/24035/medium/24035.jpg?1458191802" alt="" />			
	</div>
