<div class="com-share" data-id="24035" data-title="《外资公司纷纷盯上了中国的“油盐酱醋”市场》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/24035/medium/24035.jpg?1458191802" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/24035.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
